<span id="freeTextContainer11089413984213467396">A pretty funny account of the life of a young vet in Yorkshire, with interesting characters, both animal and human.<br/>It was a really hard world, before antibiotics and modern medicines, out in the freezing countryside at all hours, but he was content with that life, and that comes through his writing. </span>

          </span>
