        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3893591881" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8401477497372172133">If Only They Could Talk ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br/><br/>*sighs* this book is like being wrapped in a cosy blanket whilst listening to a storyteller describing their life with a cup of tea brewing at the same time. Alf Wight (James Herriot) is a fabulous raconteur and had me smiling and laughing on one page only to flip the page and burst into tears. I am so grateful for Channel 5’s new version for making me pick up this delightful little book can’t wait to read the next ones. </span>

          </span>
